{"tid":1818413,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［黃色經濟圈成功例子］紅磡1仔冰室由低調黃變為黃到出哂要","createTime":"2020-01-10T01:33:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-10T11:18:05.000Z","uid":22845,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"22c4e7a5fe3bd751215a4a76ec9679ed8f81770d","tid":1818413,"uid":22845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T01:33:33.000Z","msg":"相信紅磡手足一定有聽過<span style=\"color: gold;\">1仔冰室</span>呢檔野，一由頭到尾佢都係黃，一直有同紅土家、小黃紙（即係鄺葆賢果班）一齊搞過派飯，不過就一直都係低調黃，鋪入面文宣都冇張，生意都係一般，平時晚飯時段都係吉位多過有人坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n後來12.12果期，咁啱係佢地一週年，佢地就搞左單咁既野：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LUhtozs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLUhtozs.jpg&h=2d4ced24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n高調左，都多人留意左，觀察所見開始受到懲罰；再事隔一個月，不得了，間鋪又文宣又連儂又派月曆又捐錢箱（sorry，冇影相，廢事影到手足，遲啲補個wide shot），黃到金咁，尋晚收工想幫襯下既時候發現<span style=\"color: red;\">竟然要排隊</span>，搞到我放棄入坐，買外賣算<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我明好多黃老闆都只係心黃，但係唔敢喺鋪頭表態，驚得罪藍屍，但係事實證明：<span style=\"color: gold;\">是黃不必怕</span>，你敢行出黎，憑良心做生意，就有大把手足撐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以，我喺呢度同各位良心老闆誠懇呼籲：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">是黃不必怕，齊來變金吧！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n請大家幫手推到更多老闆見到！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n後補1仔FB link: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Onescafehk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FOnescafehk%2F&d=eKFc4b3FQa1ReKUUeYtKdCC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=078c5ec6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Onescafehk/</a>"},{"pid":"1db27607c30f397f8b33e691588cc9dd1b40decc","tid":1818413,"uid":22845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T01:34:35.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aLSQB06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaLSQB06.jpg&h=6652357a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d82ebc949f8e93d02d7e540762f68e7b618ef973","tid":1818413,"uid":163704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T01:35:02.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n[全港最大的Fact Check平台-非食店篇]集合超過400間各地區各行業的良心店<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1817378\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1817378</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"95f3dc1b9a50ca5a6a54decbcd0df5b98764557a","tid":1818413,"uid":22845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T01:35:43.000Z","msg":"sor, 打錯標題，係「出哂<span style=\"color: red;\">汁</span>」"},{"pid":"34ae474ff6c032d1eba676008351b9558e99d985","tid":1818413,"uid":22845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T01:36:03.000Z","msg":"再自推<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aLSQB06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaLSQB06.jpg&h=6652357a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d7069226425d644b74637554b6153afb047693ac","tid":1818413,"uid":22845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T01:38:43.000Z","msg":"仲要佢啲炒蛋叉燒飯、炒蛋餐肉粒飯都超好味"},{"pid":"f3e97409495cd4c082c08dde1711c6fe2ea32901","tid":1818413,"uid":135628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T01:40:22.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"403526e42a3c6f82a20804c6e037f890f06a833b","tid":1818413,"uid":6211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T01:42:46.000Z","msg":"佢仲同期改左menu加左價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過算我都叫比得服"},{"pid":"9abc09fa9876c0616ce325e99ab183421ed88335","tid":1818413,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T01:46:25.000Z","msg":"見龍門多人既可以行多兩步去1仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3111a5056f6c7e22b606dcc5bcc08b41b4dab8ab","tid":1818413,"uid":7814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T01:47:15.000Z","msg":"態度好撚閪"},{"pid":"62ac9290627c2c363aa